channel.title: Help!
channel.description:
There is a small problem. On my server, the fences are...like fighter hats with antlers. I'm using the PwnScape client and I haven't the slightest how to change it. Could somebody give me a tutorial or a suggestion on how to change them back to normal fences. Thank you.
Check the attachments.

The problem is in fact the client caches. It’s their individual item maskins. That explains the arms stretched out; uncoded item being worn. This is why I just use normal clients, with normal 317 cache ^.^
